      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a great fit for someone looking for a reliable driver that needs a little TLC. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the hood and a few minor scuffs around the bumpers. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all major electronics remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need a tune-up and new tires in the near future to ensure long-term reliability.",
