      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in an impeccable state, reflecting a level of preservation that meets the most exacting standards. Meticulously maintained and mechanically flawless, it offers an uncompromised driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast. We invite you to acquire a specimen that defines the pinnacle of its class.",
