    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe the condition of this beauty. It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like a member of the family. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found! I\u2019m looking for a new home for it where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
