      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in impeccable mechanical and cosmetic order. At the heart of this machine is the S54 3.2L inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression and featuring a documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul for peak variable valve timing precision. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers short, tactile throws, sending power to a factory variable M differential lock. The chassis is superlative, with a reinforced rear subframe and a suspension geometry that remains true to its original factory kinematics. Every bushing, seal, and heat shield is in place, reflecting a vehicle that has been maintained with an open checkbook. The exterior retains its deep luster with no evidence of panel misalignment or paint degradation, while the undercarriage is remarkably dry and free of oxidation. This is a turn-key example for the collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
